{"id":"int-4ba9df31","kind":"field_change","created_at":"2026-05-16T16:16:55.363153754Z","actor":"Hans Kohlreiter","issue_id":"claude-dev-tools-8ed","extra":{"field":"status","new_value":"closed","old_value":"in_progress","reason":"Helper script implemented and verified. All quality gates pass: bash -n clean, shellcheck clean, all 10+ ticket verification scenarios pass (multi-session, refresh idempotency, zero-gap, TTL expiry, path-traversal block, PID-reuse safety, jq shadowing robustness, non-systemd/missing-jq fallbacks). Smoke-tested live: start spawns inhibitor visible in systemd-inhibit --list with correct annotation, stop removes it cleanly. Deviation: shebang uses /usr/bin/bash absolute path (instead of /usr/bin/env bash) so the ticket's own PATH=/nowhere fallback test works correctly."}}
